description: This painting shows a girl wearing a hat and dress in front of a window. The girl looks at the viewer with her blue eyes. Her expression is one of happiness. She seems to be thinking about something happy. The window behind her is open and we can see some trees outside. There are also flowers on the ground near her feet. The background is very light and bright. The colors used in this painting are mostly blues, greens, yellows, oranges, reds, pinks, whites, grays, browns, and blacks.
